EN: We should take depression treatment seriously.

ZH: 抑郁是一种常见的心理健康问题。
EN: Depression is a common mental health issue.

ZH: 这个新药可以帮助缓解抑郁症状。
EN: This new medication can help alleviate depressive symptoms.

